def insert_after_index(lst):
    index_85 = lst.index(85)
    lst.insert(index_85 + 1, [41, 95])
    return lst

# Example usage:
given_list = [10, 20, 30, 40, 50, 85, 60, 70]
result_list = insert_after_index(given_list)
print(result_list)  # Output: [10, 20, 30, 40, 50, 85, [41, 95], 60, 70]
